    "originContent": "### 1.1 Dependencies",
    "translatedContent": "### 1.1 의존성"
  },
  {
    "row": 11,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 12,
    "rowsha": "CcIKvnqoZvAqs+E/k+5zO8CpBCx9e8jA1QA7P3Hlt0U=",
    "originContent": "Install the following packages, depending on your operating system:",
    "translatedContent": "운영 체제에 따라 다음 패키지를 설치하세요:"
  },
  {
    "row": 13,
    "rowsha": "k8HLryGfyhjAKsixx3QTCSiYimV+J40U5rAn8RU7Ceo=",
    "originContent": "  * Debian: `apt install build-essential texinfo wget`",
    "translatedContent": "  * Debian: `apt install build-essential texinfo wget`"
  },
  {
    "row": 14,
    "rowsha": "EyURoEKAdrPd9iZCPm4nti8+C/2eaQL9zrslgH6/M6c=",
    "originContent": "  * RedHat: `yum install gcc gcc-c++ texinfo-tex wget`",
    "translatedContent": "  * RedHat: `yum install gcc gcc-c++ texinfo-tex wget`"
  },
  {
    "row": 15,
    "rowsha": "xIhwdkvTRwKjzERH5mjeSen4estZX9Ac4bUd8xUk07c=",
    "originContent": "  * Arch: `pacman -S base-devel texinfo wget`",
    "translatedContent": "  * Arch: `pacman -S base-devel texinfo wget`"
  },
  {
    "row": 16,
    "rowsha": "jBENXswCQEfbvnykF2p8PqDfi5nTLEk3Pje7/Ez+Rbw=",
    "originContent": "  * Gentoo: `emerge sys-apps/texinfo net-misc/wget`",
    "translatedContent": "  * Gentoo: `emerge sys-apps/texinfo net-misc/wget`"
  },
  {
    "row": 17,
    "rowsha": "KfFxKVT6e/FUieOOkGGuMMgX7sRGuC1FmVPsOOtVZiI=",
    "originContent": "  * macOS: `xcode-select --install && brew install wget`",
    "translatedContent": "  * macOS: `xcode-select --install && brew install wget`"
  },
  {
    "row": 18,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
