  {
    "row": 26,
    "rowsha": "yz+R1U7uMOU+NbK5mQX3Dxae1Un9eJCdPawt78ntjTs=",
    "originContent": "---",
    "translatedContent": "---"
  },
  {
    "row": 27,
    "rowsha": "YOPO+NgnUEqyOltSSEIZKKDPF45h7glD4zmIXZkdd4A=",
    "originContent": "**NOTE**",
    "translatedContent": "**참고**"
  },
  {
    "row": 28,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 29,
    "rowsha": "1WVcughiS/z29R5i/XTtaEW5pEUfAiHqABN//ynlsrs=",
    "originContent": "There are two variables that control which directory Marsdev is built and installed:",
    "translatedContent": "Marsdev가 빌드되고 설치될 디렉터리를 제어하는 두 개의 변수가 있습니다:"
  },
  {
    "row": 30,
    "rowsha": "qY9wE7M1CedlXSeLsQCEFRY5iplaYxsw29EfJgyuKno=",
    "originContent": " - `MARS_BUILD_DIR` = (REPOSITORY_ROOT)/mars",
    "translatedContent": " - `MARS_BUILD_DIR` = (REPOSITORY_ROOT)/mars"
  },
  {
    "row": 31,
    "rowsha": "Gfc2o+uuMpwYiwQWs7FbXUd7hnKFi8QEo4bMMcdBtU0=",
    "originContent": " - `MARS_INSTALL_DIR` = /opt/toolchains/mars",
    "translatedContent": " - `MARS_INSTALL_DIR` = /opt/toolchains/mars"
  },
  {
    "row": 32,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 33,
    "rowsha": "PyM4218N3jRnC7zR9rUDGDc5E0iRVW0jh238DtyWx9s=",
    "originContent": "If you wish to change the location of either, use an export command like this:",
    "translatedContent": "둘 중 하나의 위치를 변경하려면 다음과 같은 export 명령을 사용하세요:"
  },
  {
    "row": 34,
    "rowsha": "xyoVQomURZwuTB5boQrlub4ZPDlymuoXG6mXQ+7BUCc=",
    "originContent": " - `export MARS_INSTALL_DIR=/path/to/mars`",
    "translatedContent": " - `export MARS_INSTALL_DIR=/path/to/mars`"
  },
  {
    "row": 35,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 36,
    "rowsha": "HKkmwIKkh/ieiMP2kW0j8EIg0q9OdFbnoA5PMx2tBTQ=",
    "originContent": "If you forget `--recurse-submodules` then run:",
    "translatedContent": "`--recurse-submodules`를 잊었다면 다음을 실행하세요:"
  },
  {
    "row": 37,
    "rowsha": "GnqY646LgalmrjYiy85EoCEcEmDQjPBNa5an3o9PfYI=",
    "originContent": " - `git submodule init && git submodule update`",
    "translatedContent": " - `git submodule init && git submodule update`"
  },
  {
    "row": 38,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 39,
    "rowsha": "84w5X0UhmKu5AWgu8jm6Dmb3R0585SU1RR0SCOlDrBM=",
    "originContent": "Also, it is **highly recommended** to use something like `-j8`, replacing the 8 with",
    "translatedContent": "또한, CPU 코어 수에 맞춰 `-j8` 같은 옵션을 사용하는 것이 **강력히 권장**됩니다."
  },
  {
    "row": 40,
    "rowsha": "7WfcRBwzjomnwk+053ZqUDZx1BSxy4H9wp1ZCO9F5Oc=",
    "originContent": "the number of CPU cores you have. I've run into weird unexplainable problems with `-j`",
    "translatedContent": "저는 `-j` 옵션 사용 시 설명할 수 없는 이상한 문제가 발생한 적이 있습니다."
  },
  {
    "row": 41,
    "rowsha": "63uDJm8KZoBmVETEewfF/9CR4jfvl+hDJ46YQn5v0Rk=",
    "originContent": "by itself, so please specify a number.",
    "translatedContent": "그 자체로는 숫자를 지정해야 합니다."
  },
  {
    "row": 42,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 43,
    "rowsha": "yz+R1U7uMOU+NbK5mQX3Dxae1Un9eJCdPawt78ntjTs=",
    "originContent": "---",
    "translatedContent": "---"
  },
  {
    "row": 44,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 45,
    "rowsha": "nsPZLZCQc67vtBNzrZtmUq/lew4S1CCJMLqq4fQbGY8=",
    "originContent": "You have 2 options for building GCC:",
    "translatedContent": "GCC를 빌드하는 방법은 2가지가 있습니다:"
  },
  {
    "row": 46,
    "rowsha": "7MbiCql39BSTnR28ZmJqdAmWqjIigKxHmdza3WXxHdA=",
    "originContent": " - `make m68k-toolchain` - Without Newlib",
    "translatedContent": " - `make m68k-toolchain` - Newlib 없이"
  },
  {
    "row": 47,
    "rowsha": "g++39d/XsvZbEFbW0IBgiR+AJ+3XseuRopZv0pxDpOU=",
    "originContent": " - `make m68k-toolchain-newlib` - With Newlib",
    "translatedContent": " - `make m68k-toolchain-newlib` - Newlib 포함"
  },
  {
    "row": 48,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 49,
    "rowsha": "wJHfyHUJYy6+XL9muTpkHxhApEYcYbmd7l5Fvjpe4EE=",
    "originContent": "For 32X, the `sh` toolchain must also be built.",
    "translatedContent": "32X의 경우, `sh` 툴체인도 빌드해야 합니다."
  },
  {
    "row": 50,
    "rowsha": "tpvPUaLsCU/I4CVp5foM+vUwfbc9k49FcUEL2O3QO3c=",
    "originContent": "The options are the same, swapping out `m68k` in the commands above with `sh`.",
    "translatedContent": "옵션은 위 명령어에서 `m68k`를 `sh`로 바꾸면 동일합니다."
  },
  {
    "row": 51,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 52,
    "rowsha": "oWopUwbtIS6awDk444K/y2y+kSQVzB7+IATVJ4NFR3k=",
    "originContent": "If you want a different GCC version, or to build specific languages:",
    "translatedContent": "다른 GCC 버전을 원하거나 특정 언어만 빌드하려면:"
  },
  {
    "row": 53,
    "rowsha": "2fpH30/ZNT/4DtDNgBov7cyoIjtgUwOuXteZCpaoXag=",
    "originContent": " - `make m68k-toolchain-newlib GCC_VER=12.4.0 LANGS=c,c++`",
    "translatedContent": " - `make m68k-toolchain-newlib GCC_VER=12.4.0 LANGS=c,c++`"
  },
  {
    "row": 54,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 55,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 56,
    "rowsha": "YQp0z8x1cnyfcy6cEGP/Ck9dAApkZkB8ujZnuzAN7i0=",
    "originContent": "### 3. (Optional) SGDK",
    "translatedContent": "### 3. (선택 사항) SGDK"
  },
  {
    "row": 57,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 58,
    "rowsha": "R3ucfRkOwkNS+KClXY+8cscNHYpXfLJfPIAgPhLaybs=",
    "originContent": "SGDK requires Java, so Install it.",
    "translatedContent": "SGDK는 자바가 필요하므로 설치하세요."
  },
  {
    "row": 59,
    "rowsha": "Nl4P/JjiPfr2k5RuWEG1GThghBAlmTLEB44J0xhXqrk=",
    "originContent": "  * Debian: `apt install openjdk-11-jre`",
    "translatedContent": "  * Debian: `apt install openjdk-11-jre`"
  },
  {
    "row": 60,
    "rowsha": "YkpbVOUKjqCDwOgUhxBhMIoM68jOIG/ePQNVAmjUHvQ=",
    "originContent": "  * RedHat: `yum install java-11-openjdk`",
    "translatedContent": "  * RedHat: `yum install java-11-openjdk`"
  },
  {
    "row": 61,
    "rowsha": "bZ32hq5DiYL7teoddBpt45oRT4jVOlx2YPdic3v375A=",
    "originContent": "  * Arch: `pacman -S jdk11-openjdk`",
    "translatedContent": "  * Arch: `pacman -S jdk11-openjdk`"
  },
  {
    "row": 62,
    "rowsha": "5zs+LSqQ5ap88g36tSwgKcHCKoOZi6cDGiLOnpBYSNY=",
    "originContent": "  * Gentoo: `emerge dev-java/openjdk`",
    "translatedContent": "  * Gentoo: `emerge dev-java/openjdk`"
  },
  {
    "row": 63,
    "rowsha": "X9zd29IgkRcuyGFegkIdQq83iFU1Y1s+IrvHj7CEHhI=",
    "originContent": "  * macOS: `brew install java`",
    "translatedContent": "  * macOS: `brew install java`"
  },
  {
    "row": 64,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 65,
    "rowsha": "yz+R1U7uMOU+NbK5mQX3Dxae1Un9eJCdPawt78ntjTs=",
    "originContent": "---",
    "translatedContent": "---"
  },
  {
    "row": 66,
    "rowsha": "iSETU3EH7+/eNQ+R25+E4w3/D3weimQSD21Kw4+5TY0=",
    "originContent": "**Note for macOS**",
    "translatedContent": "**macOS 주의 사항**"
  },
  {
    "row": 67,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 68,
    "rowsha": "iAh3rHGMJg3ZBOUns69gayZzDiNfQq2BA7l0ZG3c0ro=",
    "originContent": "OpenJDK needs to be added to the PATH.",
    "translatedContent": "OpenJDK를 PATH에 추가해야 합니다."
  },
  {
    "row": 69,
    "rowsha": "5EQ5Zbzyrwywv4lTpDVJCXgrtD62OEh7NhRZVEctKf0=",
    "originContent": " - Open `~/.zshrc` (or `~/.bashrc` if you still use bash) and add the line:",
    "translatedContent": " - `~/.zshrc` (또는 아직 bash를 사용한다면 `~/.bashrc`)를 열고 다음 줄을 추가하세요:"
  },
  {
    "row": 70,
    "rowsha": "TJYol0RgMUsKDWvJVpiAGLUqqsN88RBcCH9lu5ydTdI=",
    "originContent": "    - `export PATH=\"/usr/local/opt/openjdk/bin:$PATH\"`",
    "translatedContent": "    - `export PATH=\"/usr/local/opt/openjdk/bin:$PATH\"`"
  },
  {
    "row": 71,
    "rowsha": "3d3lkPwIZnlP0Es6e6HUbjjwMzZqPMFinQul3nkJs/4=",
    "originContent": " - Restart the terminal or run `source ~/.zshrc`",
    "translatedContent": " - 터미널을 재시작하거나 `source ~/.zshrc` 명령을 실행하세요"
  },
  {
    "row": 72,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 73,
    "rowsha": "yz+R1U7uMOU+NbK5mQX3Dxae1Un9eJCdPawt78ntjTs=",
    "originContent": "---",
    "translatedContent": "---"
  },
  {
    "row": 74,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 75,
    "rowsha": "5nF92k30oHRSK85wjHlWmVT8AeG+OzYGct/0PWSIw9c=",
    "originContent": "Build SGDK:",
    "translatedContent": "SGDK 빌드:"
  },
  {
    "row": 76,
    "rowsha": "hGrbiXu7li1iMfdeCIb+OZQYPSNLsyIn+VM34SdiVDc=",
    "originContent": " - `make sgdk`",
    "translatedContent": " - `make sgdk`"
  },
  {
    "row": 77,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 78,
    "rowsha": "8AdF6J/dQ6KWRXjWbX6K5cHUticPE/JhHBfMI+bjtco=",
    "originContent": "A specific version of SGDK can be specified with `SGDK_VER=<git tag>`,",
    "translatedContent": "특정 SGDK 버전은 `SGDK_VER=<git tag>`로 지정할 수 있지만,"
  },
  {
    "row": 79,
    "rowsha": "w0wTEhbCau1TE6Yh3zW/fdWciqs8+XlB0QsZXkLLG+o=",
    "originContent": "but I cannot guarantee versions other than the default to work.",
    "translatedContent": "기본 버전 외에는 정상 동작을 보장하지 않습니다."
  },
  {
    "row": 80,
    "rowsha": "w/zAK3fFhSjRAnC0KE1lb8TpbCPRMyNWxegCP20juTQ=",
    "originContent": "Adventurous people who want to test the latest changes can specify `SGDK_VER=master` too.",
    "translatedContent": "최신 변경 사항을 시험해보고 싶은 모험심 강한 분은 `SGDK_VER=master`도 지정할 수 있습니다."
  },
  {
    "row": 81,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
