    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 128,
    "rowsha": "hjo9Bnwid1TCnzGrG/9IG5ACtkr5WGOci92paRuLyPM=",
    "originContent": " - Grab the makefile from inside `examples/sgdk-skeleton` and drop it into your project.",
    "translatedContent": " - `examples/sgdk-skeleton` 내부의 makefile을 가져와 프로젝트에 넣으세요."
  },
  {
    "row": 129,
    "rowsha": "GDNCcxlwk7jEVO6ObxBfDf1U4C0Kubr6sk1ov10FYk4=",
    "originContent": " - `source /opt/toolchains/mars/mars.sh`",
    "translatedContent": " - `source /opt/toolchains/mars/mars.sh`"
  },
  {
    "row": 130,
    "rowsha": "vXI1WDuAy4ELEXImtw92GVqygXlFQdDSOPdXKMbPqIM=",
    "originContent": " - `make`",
    "translatedContent": " - `make`"
  },
  {
    "row": 131,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 132,
    "rowsha": "V8npEB09fpypAuAPCcOjWsFAagUKi401hftZloi8fzk=",
    "originContent": "### Can I build a Gendev project with Marsdev or vice-versa?",
    "translatedContent": "### Marsdev로 Gendev 프로젝트를 빌드하거나 그 반대도 가능한가요?"
  },
  {
    "row": 133,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 134,
    "rowsha": "NlAGkTA2zWydVc7X8kgeLZ16PP9WNwXABILGAh8yi1c=",
    "originContent": "Not easily. You'll need to mess with the Makefile to get it working.",
    "translatedContent": "쉽지 않습니다. 작동하게 하려면 Makefile을 수정해야 합니다."
  },
  {
    "row": 135,
    "rowsha": "E6vxAwoNSVLX2dOssaNbRwkaWP8WyQXZ0lZ+k1cJV0g=",
    "originContent": "Start by comparing your current Makefile to one of the example projects.",
    "translatedContent": "현재 Makefile을 예제 프로젝트 중 하나와 비교하는 것부터 시작하세요."
  },
  {
    "row": 136,
    "rowsha": "Vhl32DIpNLtDc9Vh591UsZ9husM332t2P0zonMqh88I=",
    "originContent": "The [Migration](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/andwn/marsdev/master/doc/migration.md) document may be helpful here.",
    "translatedContent": "[Migration](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/andwn/marsdev/master/doc/migration.md) 문서가 도움이 될 수 있습니다."
  },
  {
    "row": 137,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 138,
    "rowsha": "Ot/S/6wk1jja0XJd/h7c9utLFrssC/c1PrWoTTX6k8Y=",
    "originContent": "### How can I tell if an issue I'm having with SGDK is caused by Marsdev?",
    "translatedContent": "### SGDK 문제의 원인이 Marsdev인지 어떻게 알 수 있나요?"
  },
  {
    "row": 139,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 140,
    "rowsha": "PVlHaUUZHrNjzystiO0fHUF0N2xI44aBHhG0mIqbhiM=",
    "originContent": "It should be possible to compile your project as-is with an official SGDK release.",
    "translatedContent": "공식 SGDK 릴리스로 프로젝트를 그대로 컴파일할 수 있어야 합니다."
  },
  {
    "row": 141,
    "rowsha": "fDQyNYYfokBBwuemU/vOX7VCymMD6WHcXqPKbasEF/o=",
    "originContent": "The included Makefile is just a wrapper for `make -f $GDK/makefile.gen`.",
    "translatedContent": "포함된 Makefile은 단지 `make -f $GDK/makefile.gen`의 래퍼입니다."
  },
  {
    "row": 142,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 143,
    "rowsha": "k8ms9y9i1ztv7/u8SHAT2KWirgUUItvKny2lwEja64M=",
    "originContent": "If the issue persists, it's SGDK's fault. If the issue is fixed, it's Marsdev's fault.",
    "translatedContent": "문제가 계속되면 SGDK의 문제이고, 문제가 해결되면 Marsdev의 문제입니다."
  },
  {
    "row": 144,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 145,
    "rowsha": "SlDLXDpBZUdQjacaIvawuJOJEo9CcLR0uXVshwpax7Y=",
    "originContent": "### How do I use this with my favorite IDE?",
    "translatedContent": "### 내가 좋아하는 IDE에서 이걸 어떻게 사용하나요?"
  },
  {
    "row": 146,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 147,
    "rowsha": "eMUp15igEmM/+zgIvSutm8DYPWCubR19s/tZKvIFvIk=",
    "originContent": "There are so many of these, and they all have different places you have to go to configure paths.",
    "translatedContent": "IDE가 너무 많고, 각각 경로 설정을 해야 하는 위치가 다릅니다."
  },
  {
    "row": 148,
    "rowsha": "I0Wij8YF8cKSwMW4j2xq2XhSoVhupdeoIpjcUvVQGfs=",
    "originContent": "In general the only thing you should NEED to do, is point it to the headers.",
    "translatedContent": "일반적으로 해야 하는 유일한 일은 헤더 위치를 지정하는 것입니다."
  },
  {
    "row": 149,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 150,
    "rowsha": "V6lQT+IMUUwOd/LJH/czEy/3P6EqI501JQJfvwhEpho=",
    "originContent": " * GCC Headers: `$(MARSDEV)/m68k-elf/lib/gcc/m68k-elf/$(GCC_VER)/include`",
    "translatedContent": " * GCC 헤더: `$(MARSDEV)/m68k-elf/lib/gcc/m68k-elf/$(GCC_VER)/include`"
  },
  {
    "row": 151,
    "rowsha": "HTZzCClYyKeiPRG1p0783bi9WxO9L7S0ojESI+qz3b4=",
    "originContent": " * SGDK Headers: `$(MARSDEV)/m68k-elf/include`",
    "translatedContent": " * SGDK 헤더: `$(MARSDEV)/m68k-elf/include`"
  },
  {
    "row": 152,
    "rowsha": "IjCnlkCu5NvDFwx/iKsl2yHohrpQCjOR2k04dTL26l4=",
    "originContent": " * Newlib Headers: `$(MARSDEV)/m68k-elf/m68k-elf/include`",
    "translatedContent": " * Newlib 헤더: `$(MARSDEV)/m68k-elf/m68k-elf/include`"
  },
  {
    "row": 153,
    "rowsha": "Nqnn8clbgv+5l0PgxcTOldg8mkMKrFn4TvPL+rYUUGg=",
    "originContent": " ",
    "translatedContent": " "
  },
  {
    "row": 154,
    "rowsha": "z1CioUuwZw5zc1Nounn2R+qLjeEhmCzZK0mXVbJsEEc=",
    "originContent": "If your IDE lets you configure what the build/run buttons do, just have it run something like this.",
    "translatedContent": "IDE가 빌드/실행 버튼에 수행할 작업을 설정할 수 있다면, 다음과 같이 실행하게 하세요."
  },
  {
    "row": 155,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 156,
    "rowsha": "rSpM9y5SBxjISbf+i+OJH/+v4uLDUeXpq0wQ9j3WZjs=",
    "originContent": " * Build: `make MARSDEV=/path/to/mars`",
    "translatedContent": " * 빌드: `make MARSDEV=/path/to/mars`"
  },
  {
    "row": 157,
    "rowsha": "I/I/fw5BurbELxdA3wF1KkgW/6OySITFjvlwRH5x8zU=",
    "originContent": " * Run: `/path/to/an/emulator out.bin`",
    "translatedContent": " * 실행: `/path/to/an/emulator out.bin`"
  },
  {
    "row": 158,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 159,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 160,
    "rowsha": "ITlkyZ9sYIxgSKLrpJ9nz5c3K5IVJEqPkV/OmAyx2tc=",
    "originContent": "### What about Windows?",
    "translatedContent": "### 윈도우는 어떻게 하나요?"
  },
  {
    "row": 161,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "[WSL](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/wsl/install)을 사용하는 것을 강력히 권장하며  "
  },
  {
    "row": 162,
    "rowsha": "P7n5uIG04GuW2EZJ1RUc+Zyqc2EbBB9WmgvMUkzC4Zw=",
    "originContent": "I highly recommend using [WSL](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/wsl/install)",
    "translatedContent": "Debian에 대한 지침을 따르세요.  "
  },
  {
    "row": 163,
    "rowsha": "lXwhQtzq9aoNd8SQzTOKBYTPgwKnPb+Y+M5pOmoE8Xk=",
    "originContent": "and follow the instructions for Debian.",
    "translatedContent": "다른 사람이 기여한 Dockerfile을 사용해 볼 수도 있지만  "
  },
  {
    "row": 164,
    "rowsha": "5ERUdfDwJ6rNYfp92VUGfP+90D/CdEoxcA894CEBGRI=",
    "originContent": "You could also try using the Dockerfile, although that is contributed by others",
    "translatedContent": "저는 직접 테스트하지 않았습니다.  "
  },
  {
    "row": 165,
    "rowsha": "s/bWHvqs3KfSLg/3vWNEWVMFabvkPHmQvedxqiQd5ik=",
    "originContent": "and I don't test it myself.",
    "translatedContent": "예전에는 [MSYS2](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/andwn/marsdev/master/doc/install_msys_legacy.md)를 사용했는데,  "
