    "row": 166,
    "rowsha": "mh7I0CAqvLo+ffQMEYGeOQ58Z7I18wm/ht9AeB7SndA=",
    "originContent": "I used to use [MSYS2](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/andwn/marsdev/master/doc/install_msys_legacy.md), but how slow and clunky it is can not be overstated.",
    "translatedContent": "그것이 얼마나 느리고 무거운지 과장할 수 없습니다.  "
