    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "### 저는 /opt에 설치하는 것을 좋아하지 않습니다. 예전의 ~/mars 방식이 좋습니다  "
  },
  {
    "row": 172,
    "rowsha": "85mKK6ZePI3s8ueJt/EFcTJMelBCyr1JgWw7NBmIOvA=",
    "originContent": "### I don't like installing to /opt. I want the old ~/mars way back",
    "translatedContent": "  "
  },
  {
    "row": 173,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "간단합니다.  "
  },
  {
    "row": 174,
    "rowsha": "xgqoOHyUzINZtR+F1XtmG/YBIB4aUsa5nFld0IFIwjg=",
    "originContent": "That's easy.",
    "translatedContent": "1. `export MARS_BUILD_DIR=${HOME}/mars`  "
  },
  {
    "row": 175,
    "rowsha": "bQQR+ZKmbi/6A5Exq0mOGQ/xPDeP+cqbOCS8+3oGdjc=",
    "originContent": "1. `export MARS_BUILD_DIR=${HOME}/mars`",
    "translatedContent": "2. 1단계부터 4단계까지 정상적으로 진행하세요  "
  },
  {
    "row": 176,
    "rowsha": "m7ORiMDz15oWS6RHSf/sAkIQP0eR5TkKqG6v8F4g+1o=",
    "originContent": "2. Do steps 1 - 4 normally",
    "translatedContent": "3. 설치 단계는 건너뛰고 대신 `~/.bashrc`에 다음을 추가하세요:"
  },
  {
    "row": 177,
    "rowsha": "A1etjuyyWjiT1XC5a5FYpht7Gf9yls6eOI9PoYMGhNg=",
    "originContent": "3. Skip the installation step, instead add to your `~/.bashrc`:",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 178,
    "rowsha": "8bkBhHOQsO1+N058HkZOwXtGpCfEh6WtbL0pBkBQg9U=",
    "originContent": "```",
    "translatedContent": "```"
  },
  {
    "row": 179,
    "rowsha": "N77Ti3OHmpTtNe/mTx+4GC9gFEeyskmAxC5ZWARWuns=",
    "originContent": "export MARSDEV=${HOME}/mars",
    "translatedContent": "export MARSDEV=${HOME}/mars"
  },
  {
    "row": 180,
    "rowsha": "6BvLoolhGsum+hS3a4D3VYsaV6XcbrSLRDFqNmdFNBA=",
    "originContent": "export GDK=${MARSDEV}/m68k-elf",
    "translatedContent": "export GDK=${MARSDEV}/m68k-elf"
  },
